OK, here's one of mine. I bought 6 buses from a wrecking yard a few years
back for a 1000 dollars. With the help of VW Howard and Cory I got 3 of them
home and a lot of parts off the others. After selling what I could I ended
up getting paid 1000 to own my 1960 DD, which was all I was after anyway. So
a few people got a couple buses and a lot of parts for a really good deal (I
only wanted to get my money back) and I ended up with the DD I currently
drive and some extra money to put it together.

ronnie

ps. I did buy a 64 Kombi, running driving with hippy interior here in Havasu
a long time ago for $150.00 and I still have it.

